description: A Chromium-based WPF/WinForms component that can be embedded into your .NET application to display modern web pages built with HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Silverlight etc.
releaseNotes:
DotNetBrowser 1.5.1 contains the following features and improvements:
    Support of HiDPI monitors on Windows 8/8.1/10 has been implemented.
    The issue with wrong Target attribute in DOMEventListener has been fixed.
    The deadlock issue when close parent of popup window has been fixed.
    The deadlock issue when display File Save/Open dialog has been fixed.
    Web page loading time has been improved.
summary: Solution for integration of Chromium-based component into .NET applications.
title: DotNetBrowser
